_sText:
This is the edited version of fy_castle_battle. Map was created by Shark62808 and the .nav file was created by Chizbone. The map takes place in a castle. There are a total of 60 spawnpoints. The T's spawn in the dungeon while the CT's spawn in the front yard.
Changes made
  • added more props
  • edited some of the lighting
  • added a 3D skybox
  • Chizbone edited the .nav file
  • made reflections in floor more visible
  • added a camera outside and a monitor above the fireplace
